                                      {
                                          "gid":  "1797820624591921",
                                          "title":  "Achievements Added to Splinter Cell Blacklist",
                                          "url":  "https://steamstore-a.akamaihd.net/news/externalpost/steam_community_announcements/1797820624591921",
                                          "is_external_url":  true,
                                          "author":  "UbiArcane",
                                          "contents":  "Agents,\n\nWe are pleased to announce that Steam Achievements are now available for Splinter Cell: Blacklist!\n\nAs a heads up, achievements will be retroactively earned for the accomplishments already completed in your game. For the sync to happen, you need to launch the game once. Once synced, the previously unlocked Ubisoft Connect achievements will be automatically unlocked on Steam. \n\nTo ensure that you can complete 100% of the Steam Achievements for Splinter Cell: Blacklist, we\u0027ve removed 19 achievements that required online services that are no longer available for the game.\n",
